00:30:25,050 --> 00:30:31,332
♫  Memories also detach with it  ♫

261
00:30:32,040 --> 00:30:33,940
 Gu Yi!  
 ♫  This air   ♫

262
00:30:34,640 --> 00:30:37,520
 Gu Yi!  
 ♫  Smothers me  ♫

